{"tid":1381110,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次 和理非為矛 勇武為盾！","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:57:06.000Z","uid":287012,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3818e6e58f4ce5c931491193761d5073e38f13fd","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"的而且確 727 728係因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心雄同戀戰！</span></span></strong><br />\n721我地打左場漂亮嘅勝仗 前線完全守住班狗嘅推進 <br />\n催淚彈 無人驚<br />\n橡膠彈 無人驚<br />\n警犬推進 無人驚<br />\n不斷敲打而士氣好好<br />\n正式將光復香港 時代革命變成口號<br />\n但就因為咁727 728就無目的地留守同送頭<br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非為盾</span></span>做原因 令多啲人留守<br />\n結果就機動性低而多左前線被補<br />\n無左以前個種完成任務就走嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">be water</span></span><br />\nBe water應該攻守兼備 互相配合<br />\n之前勇武回合 勇武為矛 和理非為盾<br />\n依家和理非回合<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非為矛 勇武為盾</span></span><br />\n適時轉下way 令敵人難以適應<br />\n所以<br />\n和理非要比心機！<br />\n不合作運動 罷工！<br />\n利申: 我都係前線後少少 滅下彈救下人<br />\n唔敢做肉盾 唔敢企最前 sorry<br />\n727 728都覺得應該要留到最後<br />\n都屌下身邊啲fd做乜走<br />\n但過後惗翻都係有啲戀戰<br />\n我估大部份post都唔係想分化 係真係激動姐<br />\n大家繼續檢討 繼續進步<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec989d48988c2a256b2acc6d76d06b2e349bd292","tid":1381110,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"91d20f62b24d70bfa1aa98e55fd9651d81d3eae7","tid":1381110,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:28:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"d30acd4674bbfe71cc5a351dc267533e2556f902","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48c7788e4ccada6cd03e6307e1be5d5a48f606b4","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"757ac5637013e997c584338f8ad8a084ce474ab2","tid":1381110,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&amp;新界東夾擊大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381144</a>"},{"pid":"d047a7a76c10f59e548b323c4dea4a74e831e689","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"178d9b688e08e07a41986add6ef0983bc12a043b","tid":1381110,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"757ac5637013e997c584338f8ad8a084ce474ab2","tid":1381110,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&amp;新界東夾擊大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381144</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"幫推 Plz"},{"pid":"dd96770b0816416c932a89bde50ea9f0ba7eee94","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b5bcc3380c5ce6b95956e3435738670523fde10f","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9e58c8ad2dce13c49774614faa9716da24d3105c","tid":1381110,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20e5ddf4c5a57b09ee8de29c3308234afefefaf1","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8ab8535c4a1ce3c90bf40e81d358522066929f29","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"3644068793ee3640eb39d54c12c692173d36b8c1","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d5b55ca4b915cd28bee76b70148d40f969c238dc","tid":1381110,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n攻守可以視情況互換<br />\n嚟緊個趨勢 警方係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會</span></strong>比不反對通知書<br />\n前線可以係路線中間揀定個易守難攻嘅位築起一道防線<br />\n防線預留位置比遊行人士通過<br />\n遊行人士就和理非<br />\n到警察趕嘅就慢慢退返防線<br />\n可以返起點走又或者Backup前線<br />\n等遊行群眾可以安全撤離<br />\n<br />\n優點有三<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 勇武 和理非分工清晰 合作難度低 減低互屌分化機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n勇武定位就係直面警察，比和理非可以安全撤離<br />\n和理非負責嗌口號，傳遞訊息比嗰區嘅人知道<br />\n唔好忘記運動一開始嘅成功係因為勇武同和理非嘅合作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 前線可以保留體力，更長時間築起防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n勇武唔洗參與全個遊行，節省體力<br />\n遊行前預先決定防線位置，到場直接開始建立防線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 和理非遊行被警察驅趕，加強雞蛋高牆嘅對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n幾次警察嘅記者會都講話係示威者使用暴力在先，警察逼不得已先採取最低武力，已經非常克制<br />\n我地就利用和理非，完全0威脅，警察一武力驅趕就可以撕破佢嘅假面具"},{"pid":"e42d8613004851356e3d029e3f8b4805d29f7c66","tid":1381110,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"我地連罷工、老豆接仔放工都未試<br />\n香港人 唔好放棄!<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n*7月30 : 地鐵不合作運動 <br />\n*8月2 : 公務員罷工集會<br />\n*8月5 : 一齊罷工 7區集會 <br />\n返工放工幫手air drop<br />\n停止前線義士受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n我要真普選 不要空降假特首"},{"pid":"0186cf70276defe05a97e3c16b3a6ac96bde5578","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"87adac19d514feed7eede82666ef9aa156e5c174","tid":1381110,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec989d48988c2a256b2acc6d76d06b2e349bd292","tid":1381110,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"我要塞車"},{"pid":"d606526482b02890b5ea63fdea3dabd6c69601d8","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"582728c2bb4aa229b60debfcb1529bcc0403758c","tid":1381110,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"805f6bdae14ea424389b64341ba6bb5e432874ba","tid":1381110,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87adac19d514feed7eede82666ef9aa156e5c174","tid":1381110,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec989d48988c2a256b2acc6d76d06b2e349bd292","tid":1381110,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"我要塞車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"我要搭地鐵"},{"pid":"ae18c72eb7efd317e500a15cd2567e00ec6c9839","tid":1381110,"uid":287012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUSA3vH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUSA3vH.png&h=8b724214&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee61d13de50c47d0ce9aee1164b8306f45a71edb","tid":1381110,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"其實真係勇武做盾<br />\n次次睇直播都見到啲勇武殿後俾和理非走先（或者話俾和理非拋棄）<br />\n望住啲勇武嘅手足俾狗扑頭先後拘捕<br />\n唔係想分化但睇到就心Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f3b6fbfdc7ed1f7cfd08fd05ee02d0c8b681fb","tid":1381110,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"我要罷工！"},{"pid":"48ba295d38bd6fc99fe392abac1ddf4a28a8dba3","tid":1381110,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee61d13de50c47d0c